Phoebe Nicholls https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phoebe_Nicholls 0 Phoebe Sarah Nicholls (born 1957) is an English film, television, and stage actress. She is known for her roles as Cordelia Flyte in Brideshead Revisited and as the mother of John Merrick in The Elephant Man.
